their children...

118
00:10:30,343 --> 00:10:32,971
because my own was banished.

119
00:10:35,481 --> 00:10:37,972
I'm sorry.

120
00:10:38,051 --> 00:10:39,541
I'm so sorry.

121
00:10:41,554 --> 00:10:43,886
Tiny mites...

122
00:10:43,957 --> 00:10:46,619
and soured dispositions.

123
00:10:48,294 --> 00:10:50,023
I've no need of them, Connor,

124
00:10:50,096 --> 00:10:51,893
any of them.

125
00:10:56,869 --> 00:10:58,894
Then it's settled.

126
00:10:58,972 --> 00:11:00,303
You're coming with me.

127
00:11:05,011 --> 00:11:07,002
[Wind Blows]

128
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,012
Aah!

129
00:11:08,081 --> 00:11:09,776
Connor!

130
00:11:09,849 --> 00:11:11,339
