142
00:11:38,244 --> 00:11:40,007
I stood at your ordination.

143
00:11:40,079 --> 00:11:41,478
I vouched for you.

144
00:11:41,547 --> 00:11:43,310
You shouldn't have
come back, Connor.

145
00:11:43,383 --> 00:11:44,748
(Priest)Take him.

146
00:11:45,985 --> 00:11:46,917
Aah!

147
00:11:48,621 --> 00:11:50,555
(Priest Speaking,
Indistinctly)

148
00:11:55,128 --> 00:11:56,618
(Priest)The ties of blood...

149
00:11:56,696 --> 00:12:01,633
