by word or deed.

150
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,829
[Gasps]

151
00:12:08,908 --> 00:12:10,341
(Connor)Mother.

152
00:12:10,410 --> 00:12:12,275
(Jacob)Due to
the infinite compassion...

153
00:12:14,680 --> 00:12:19,310
