to one final opportunity...

154
00:12:19,385 --> 00:12:21,319
to renounce all that is unholy,

155
00:12:21,387 --> 00:12:25,915
and declare Connor MacLeod
not of your loins.

156
00:12:27,527 --> 00:12:29,324
How say you,
Caiolin MacLeod?

157
00:12:31,164 --> 00:12:33,928
If your God...

158
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:38,130
should persecute me
into the next world,

159
00:12:38,204 --> 00:12:41,196
then I shall simply have
to find myself another.

160
00:12:41,274 --> 00:12:42,434
[Gasps]

161
00:12:42,508 --> 00:12:43,873
[Crowd Muttering]

162
00:12:43,943 --> 00:12:45,274
(Woman)Burn her.

163
00:12:45,344 --> 00:12:47,676
No! No! No!

164
00:12:49,382 --> 00:12:50,974
(Jacob)He is your son.

165
00:12:52,051 --> 00:12:53,985
