174
00:13:37,830 --> 00:13:39,559
[Screaming]

175
00:13:47,874 --> 00:13:48,806
[Grunts]

176
00:13:49,942 --> 00:13:51,773
(Man)
You're next,you demon.

177
00:14:01,154 --> 00:14:02,348
Aah!

178
00:14:04,257 --> 00:14:05,519
[Growling]

179
00:14:11,597 --> 00:14:13,861
(Horse Neighs)

180
00:14:24,377 --> 00:14:25,309
Aah!

181
00:14:28,114 --> 00:14:30,344
My water horse.

182
00:14:48,234 --> 00:14:49,462
Unh!

183
00:14:53,839 --> 00:14:56,103
