188
00:15:18,431 --> 00:15:19,921
Please.

189
00:15:19,999 --> 00:15:22,058
Do not leave me.

190
00:15:23,302 --> 00:15:24,963
Father.

191
00:15:36,682 --> 00:15:38,149
Aah!

192
