ware housed like
rotting pieces of meat.

218
00:20:12,491 --> 00:20:13,719
Tell me,

219
00:20:13,792 --> 00:20:16,852
is this...the better way?

220
00:20:16,929 --> 00:20:21,491
(Kell)I'm sure you'e had
time to reflect upon it.

221
00:20:22,601 --> 00:20:25,069
What you need to understand...

222
00:20:25,137 --> 00:20:28,004
is that I don't care
about the game.

223
00:20:28,073 --> 00:20:30,541
I don't care about the rules.

224
00:20:30,609 --> 00:20:34,101
I don't even care about
these pathetic souls...

225
00:20:34,179 --> 00:20:39,378
you keep locked away
as a barrier to the prize.

226
00:20:39,451 --> 00:20:43,888
Which one is
Connor MacLeod?

227
00:20:54,533 --> 00:20:56,933
[Whistling]

228
00:21:08,047 --> 00:21:08,979
[Grunts]

229
00:21:14,453 --> 00:21:15,852
[Strained Breathing]

230
00:21:47,353 --> 00:21:49,287
Well,what do we do now?

231
00:21:49,355 --> 00:21:51,789
What we always do.

232
00:21:51,857 --> 00:21:53,984
We're Watchers, not cops.

233
00:21:54,059 --> 00:21:56,220
