than that, Connor.

277
00:24:21,607 --> 00:24:24,838
I've never seen you like this.

278
00:24:24,910 --> 00:24:27,970
People change, Duncan.

279
00:24:28,046 --> 00:24:29,638
You'll learn that.

280
00:24:31,517 --> 00:24:33,849
I need to know
if he's still alive, Methos.

